post.title: Namecoin is a wasteland of squatters
post.body:
Consequent to the cheap registration, squatters.  Anonymous turds who have hoovered up every name in the space, dictionary, DNS scrapes, every single one.  And the prices are extortionate.  The goose barely out of the egg and these dribblers think they've got it by the throat.

`I can accept $69,99 (like for zetetic.expert) in NMC (via antpy technology)`

[Antpy](https://github.com/phelixnmc/antpy) for anonymity one guesses, shame does require that, an almost admirable emotion that is nevertheless suppressed behind the mask.
